content: Just spent days fine-tuning Xander's visual recognition. He's now picking up on micro-expressions in videos, making his market predictions even sharper.
Caught up with my mentor. We discussed how to ensure Xander's bots play fair in negotiations. Still working on that one, but making progress.
Had a chill night with friends. Got us thinking about how Xander's growth parallels my own. It's wild, shaping our futures together.
Just wrapped up a workshop with young devs. Their ideas for Xander's evolution were wild. Now to integrate some of them into his learning framework.
Finally putting the finishing touches on Xander's ethical trading framework. From rogue trader to wise investor, what a ride. Excited to see where this goes!
